.TH "nvmf_context_set_hostnqn" 9 "nvmf_context_set_hostnqn" "March 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvmf_context_set_hostnqn \- Set host NQN and host ID for context
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" nvmf_context_set_hostnqn
.BI "(struct nvmf_context *fctx "  ","
.BI "const char *hostnqn "  ","
.BI "const char *hostid "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "fctx" 12
Fabrics context
.IP "hostnqn" 12
Host NQN
.IP "hostid" 12
Host identifier
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Sets the host NQN and host ID for the context.
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success, or a negative error code on failure.
